1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:09,075
( wind blowing )

2
00:00:13,246 --> 00:00:15,348
♪

3
00:00:24,157 --> 00:00:25,425
Tonpetty: FOR THREE YEARS,

4
00:00:25,491 --> 00:00:28,662
YOU HAVE ENDURED
AND SURVIVED OUR TRAINING.

5
00:00:28,695 --> 00:00:31,532
YOU CAN RUN
FOR UNIMAGINABLE DISTANCES

6
00:00:31,598 --> 00:00:34,034
AND NOT BE SHORT OF BREATH.

7
00:00:34,100 --> 00:00:36,436
SOON YOU WILL BE READY TO BEGIN

8
00:00:36,503 --> 00:00:40,641
THE INTENSE TRAINING
THAT WE CALL THE CELESTIAL GATE.

9
00:00:40,707 --> 00:00:43,977
BUT I WARN YOU AGAIN, ZEPPELI,

10
00:00:44,044 --> 00:00:48,214
IF YOUR CHOICE IS TO CONTINUE
WITH THESE TEACHINGS,

11
00:00:48,314 --> 00:00:51,351
YOU WILL BE SEALING YOUR FATE.

12
00:00:51,384 --> 00:00:54,020
THE TIME TO TURN BACK IS NOW.

13
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:55,021
YOU'RE YOUNG.

14
00:00:55,055 --> 00:00:57,323
YOU CAN START A NEW LIFE.

15
00:00:57,390 --> 00:01:00,126
Zeppeli: MASTER TONPETTY,

16
00:01:00,193 --> 00:01:02,969
READ THE WAVES OF MY LIFE.

17
00:01:03,036 --> 00:01:05,371
TELL ME HOW LONG I HAVE.

18
00:01:05,405 --> 00:01:08,374
WHEN IS THIS LIFE OF MINE
GOING TO END?

19
00:01:08,407 --> 00:01:09,909
WHERE DOES IT END?

20
00:01:10,010 --> 00:01:11,712
HOW DOES IT END?

21
00:01:12,813 --> 00:01:14,915
Tonpetty: WHY DO YOU WANT
THIS KNOWLEDGE?

22
00:01:15,015 --> 00:01:19,219
Zeppeli: I BELIEVE THERE IS
A PURPOSE TO MY LIFE,

23
00:01:19,252 --> 00:01:22,022
ONE THAT I CANNOT SET ASIDE.

24
00:01:22,088 --> 00:01:25,926
I NEED TO KNOW
SO I CAN FULFILL THAT PURPOSE.

25
00:01:26,026 --> 00:01:29,663
IF I KNOW HOW MUCH TIME
I HAVE TO ACCOMPLISH IT,

26
00:01:29,730 --> 00:01:31,565
THEN I CAN ACCEPT THE OUTCOME.

27
00:01:31,598 --> 00:01:34,568
I WILL ACCEPT IT.

28
00:01:34,601 --> 00:01:37,604
Zeppeli: SO LET IT BE DONE,

29
00:01:37,704 --> 00:01:41,074
IF THAT IS WHAT YOU BELIEVE.

30
00:01:41,107 --> 00:01:42,676
KNOW THIS.

31
00:01:42,743 --> 00:01:44,711
♪

32
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,715
( Zeppeli grunts )

33
00:01:52,352 --> 00:01:54,020
IN AN ANCIENT CHAMBER,

34
00:01:54,087 --> 00:01:56,890
HIDDEN FROM THE LIGHT
AND REEKING OF DEATH,

35
00:01:56,957 --> 00:02:00,534
A CHILD
SHALL OPEN THE WAY FOR YOU.

36
00:02:00,601 --> 00:02:02,703
TO UNCHAIN A YOUNG LION

37
00:02:02,769 --> 00:02:06,306
AND RELEASE HIM
INTO THE FUTURE OF HIS DESTINY,

38
00:02:06,406 --> 00:02:08,809
YOU WILL BURN YOUR OWN WOUNDS.

39
00:02:08,875 --> 00:02:11,645
THEN FREELY
WILL YOU OPEN YOUR ARMS

40
00:02:11,745 --> 00:02:15,782
TO THE CRUEL DEATH
THAT AWAITS YOU.

41
00:02:15,816 --> 00:02:17,483
‐ ( JoJo grunts )
‐ ( Tarukus growls )

42
00:02:18,652 --> 00:02:21,221
Speedwagon: BARON ZEPPELI,

43
00:02:21,287 --> 00:02:23,389
BE CAREFUL, MY FRIEND.

44
00:02:23,456 --> 00:02:26,627
( Zeppeli breathes deeply )

45
00:02:27,594 --> 00:02:29,229
HERE I COME, JOJO.

46
00:02:29,295 --> 00:02:31,131
♪

47
00:02:33,634 --> 00:02:35,902
"TO UNCHAIN A YOUNG LION

48
00:02:35,969 --> 00:02:39,139
AND RELEASE HIM INTO
THE FUTURE OF HIS DESTINY..."

49
00:02:39,172 --> 00:02:41,174
♪

50
00:02:48,414 --> 00:02:50,684
( singing in Japanese )

51
00:04:13,379 --> 00:04:15,281
♪

52
00:04:22,122 --> 00:04:23,790
( JoJo gasping )

53
00:04:23,890 --> 00:04:26,059
CAN'T BUDGE THIS COLLAR.

54
00:04:26,126 --> 00:04:27,227
STRANGE.

55
00:04:27,293 --> 00:04:29,730
FOR SOME REASON,
TARUKUS HASN'T MADE A DISPLAY

56
00:04:29,796 --> 00:04:32,265
OF HIS TRICKS
FOR FIGHTING IN THIS ROOM.

57
00:04:32,298 --> 00:04:33,967
THAT WORRIES ME.

58
00:04:34,067 --> 00:04:35,935
Tarukus: COME TO ME, FOOLS.

59
00:04:35,969 --> 00:04:38,772
YOU THINK YOUR HAMON
WILL DO ANY GOOD?

60
00:04:38,805 --> 00:04:41,575
YOU LITTLE BUGS
CAN'T LAY A FINGER ON ME,

61
00:04:41,642 --> 00:04:43,610
NO MATTER HOW HARD YOU MAY TRY!

62
00:04:43,644 --> 00:04:45,245
HUH?

63
00:04:45,311 --> 00:04:46,479
YOU AFRAID?

64
00:04:46,547 --> 00:04:48,148
GONNA SOIL YOURSELF?!

65
00:04:48,248 --> 00:04:51,051
♪

66
00:04:55,989 --> 00:04:57,591
‐ ( chain rattles )
‐ ( Tarukus growls )

67
00:04:57,658 --> 00:04:59,826
Speedwagon:
MASTERFULLY PLAYED, BARON.

68
00:05:01,768 --> 00:05:04,771
( Tarukus roars )

69
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,575
Zeppeli: HERE WE GO!

70
00:05:08,642 --> 00:05:09,643
HOW ABOUT THIS?!

71
00:05:09,676 --> 00:05:12,178
TORNADO OVERDRIVE!

72
00:05:13,246 --> 00:05:14,848
JoJo: WATCH YOUR BACK!

73
00:05:16,082 --> 00:05:17,751
Zeppeli:
HE'S ATTACKING FROM ABOVE?

74
00:05:17,818 --> 00:05:20,821
JoJo: NO, ZEPPELI!
HE'S COMING FROM BELOW!

75
00:05:20,854 --> 00:05:22,155
( Zeppeli grunts )

76
00:05:22,188 --> 00:05:24,324
Tarukus: WHAT DO YOU KNOW?
YOU'RE BOTH RIGHT.

77
00:05:24,357 --> 00:05:25,692
( Zeppeli gasps )

78
00:05:25,759 --> 00:05:29,696
Tarukus: I CALL IT
"HELL HEAVEN SNAKE KILL."

79
00:05:29,763 --> 00:05:32,198
( Zeppeli groans )

80
00:05:32,298 --> 00:05:33,433
( Speedwagon gasps )

81
00:05:33,499 --> 00:05:35,201
( JoJo gagging )

82
00:05:35,301 --> 00:05:36,837
( Tarukus laughs )

83
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:39,372
LOVELY WATCHING YOU SUFFOCATE.

84
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:46,847
Zeppeli: I‐‐I CAN'T BREATHE.

85
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:49,550
MY HAMON WON'T MANIFEST.

86
00:05:49,650 --> 00:05:51,718
( Tarukus growls )

87
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,234
( Speedwagon screams )

88
00:06:04,705 --> 00:06:07,240
( gasping )

89
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:09,643
Zeppeli: JO‐‐

90
00:06:09,710 --> 00:06:12,646
JOJO...

91
00:06:12,713 --> 00:06:13,747
( groans )

92
00:06:13,847 --> 00:06:15,982
( chain rattles )

93
00:06:18,652 --> 00:06:20,320
( Tarukus grunts )

94
00:06:20,386 --> 00:06:23,256
♪

95
00:06:27,393 --> 00:06:30,764
LORD DIO, AS YOU ORDERED,

96
00:06:30,831 --> 00:06:33,166
THEY'RE DEAD, BOTH OF THEM.

97
00:06:33,233 --> 00:06:35,569
( Speedwagon gasps )
THIS IS‐‐

98
00:06:35,602 --> 00:06:38,772
THIS BLOODY SAVAGERY
IS UNBELIEVABLE!

99
00:06:38,872 --> 00:06:40,206
( gasps )

100
00:06:40,273 --> 00:06:45,345
( wails )

101
00:06:49,916 --> 00:06:51,718
( JoJo gasping )

102
00:06:51,785 --> 00:06:53,119
Tarukus: HMM?

103
00:06:53,186 --> 00:06:54,120
( grunts )

104
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,591
( Speedwagon gasps )

105
00:06:57,624 --> 00:06:58,692
JONATHAN!

106
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:00,293
( JoJo groaning )

107
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,635
( Tarukus growls )

108
00:07:01,735 --> 00:07:03,770
EVEN WITH A BROKEN NECK,

109
00:07:03,804 --> 00:07:07,473
YOU HAVE THE POOR TASTE
TO STILL BE ALIVE?

110
00:07:07,574 --> 00:07:09,475
ALLOW ME TO FINISH YOU OFF.

111
00:07:13,246 --> 00:07:15,481
( growls )

112
00:07:15,549 --> 00:07:18,084
Zeppeli: JO‐‐

113
00:07:18,151 --> 00:07:19,485
JOJO.

114
00:07:19,553 --> 00:07:20,987
( Tarukus grunts )

115
00:07:21,054 --> 00:07:23,824
LIVELY FOR ONLY HALF A MAN.

116
00:07:24,825 --> 00:07:27,060
Zeppeli: FREELY I GIVE THIS.

117
00:07:28,094 --> 00:07:29,830
FREELY I GIVE THIS.

118
00:07:30,764 --> 00:07:33,499
FREELY I GIVE THIS TO YOU!

119
00:07:33,567 --> 00:07:36,236
MY ULTIMATE TECHNIQUE!

120
00:07:36,302 --> 00:07:39,239
JOJO, TAKE IT!

121
00:07:39,305 --> 00:07:41,341
MAKE IT YOURS!

122
00:07:41,441 --> 00:07:43,777
( heart beating )

123
00:07:43,844 --> 00:07:47,814
ULTIMATE DEEP PASS OVERDRIVE!

124
00:07:47,848 --> 00:07:50,350
( JoJo gasps )

125
00:07:50,450 --> 00:07:52,786
( screams )

126
00:07:52,853 --> 00:07:55,789
( Zeppeli screams )

127
00:07:55,856 --> 00:07:57,591
( Speedwagon gasping )

128
00:08:11,978 --> 00:08:13,046
Zeppeli: DONE.

129
00:08:13,113 --> 00:08:15,949
JOJO, I HAVE PASSED ON TO YOU

130
00:08:16,016 --> 00:08:20,353
ALL THE HAMON WHICH WAS MINE
TO CONTROL IN THIS LIFE.

131
00:08:23,156 --> 00:08:25,291
( Speedwagon gasping )

132
00:08:28,128 --> 00:08:30,897
GO, DEAR FRIEND.

133
00:08:32,666 --> 00:08:33,734
GO.

134
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:36,136
BARON ZEPPELI!

135
00:08:36,202 --> 00:08:38,338
‐ ( wailing )
‐ ( footsteps thudding )

136
00:08:45,211 --> 00:08:46,747
Tarukus: A TOUCHING DISPLAY,

137
00:08:46,813 --> 00:08:49,850
BUT I'M STILL GOING
TO GRIND YOU INTO RED PAS‐‐

138
00:08:49,916 --> 00:08:51,585
( gags )

139
00:08:55,221 --> 00:08:57,157
♪

140
00:09:01,101 --> 00:09:03,436
Tarukus: YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

141
00:09:05,071 --> 00:09:07,741
Speedwagon: WHAT?
HE HAULED TARUKUS OFF THE GROUND

142
00:09:07,774 --> 00:09:09,242
LIKE A SACK OF TURNIPS.

143
00:09:09,275 --> 00:09:12,846
IT'S AS IF THE BARON'S HAMON
HEALED HIS BROKEN NECK.

144
00:09:12,913 --> 00:09:15,115
‐ ( JoJo grunting )
‐ Tarukus: NUMSKULL.

145
00:09:15,181 --> 00:09:18,218
YOU ACTUALLY THINK
YOU CAN YANK THAT COLLAR OPEN?

146
00:09:18,284 --> 00:09:20,420
YOU PATHETIC WASTE OF FLESH.

147
00:09:20,453 --> 00:09:22,689
I COULDN'T PULL APART
THOSE STEEL BANDS,

148
00:09:22,756 --> 00:09:26,627
EVEN WITH ALL THE POWER
GIVEN TO ME BY LORD DIO.

149
00:09:26,693 --> 00:09:29,062
( JoJo grunting )

150
00:09:31,765 --> 00:09:34,601
OH, NO, TARUKUS?!

151
00:09:37,538 --> 00:09:38,705
Speedwagon: JONATHAN!

152
00:09:38,772 --> 00:09:40,206
( Tarukus groans )

153
00:09:40,273 --> 00:09:42,108
YOU BUG, HOW'D‐‐

154
00:09:44,244 --> 00:09:46,713
JoJo: TWISTED BY MADNESS.

155
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,615
NO HUMAN FEELING.

156
00:09:48,649 --> 00:09:50,383
YOU GAVE UP YOUR REDEMPTION

157
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:53,086
WHEN YOU CHOSE
TO FOLLOW DIO, TARUKUS.

158
00:09:53,153 --> 00:09:55,288
( Tarukus chuckles )

159
00:09:55,321 --> 00:09:56,723
( roars )

160
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:58,992
( JoJo breathes deeply )

161
00:10:03,704 --> 00:10:05,606
( yells )

162
00:10:05,672 --> 00:10:07,874
( Tarukus grunts )

163
00:10:07,941 --> 00:10:10,577
( screams )

164
00:10:10,611 --> 00:10:11,912
Speedwagon: LOOK AT THAT.

165
00:10:11,945 --> 00:10:13,413
HIS HAMON'S VISIBLE.

166
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:16,216
HIS BODY CAN BARELY
CONTAIN ITS STRENGTH.

167
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:18,218
THE BARON'S HAMON JOINED

168
00:10:18,284 --> 00:10:20,887
AND MULTIPLIED INCREDIBLY
WITH JONATHAN'S.

169
00:10:20,954 --> 00:10:23,123
THERE'S BEEN NOTHING
LIKE THIS EVER!

170
00:10:23,223 --> 00:10:26,627
JoJo: TARUKUS, YOU CANNOT
BE ALLOWED TO CONTINUE.

171
00:10:26,727 --> 00:10:28,461
THIS IS CLEAR.

172
00:10:28,562 --> 00:10:30,797
YOUR EVIL SPIRIT
MUST BE BANISHED!

173
00:10:30,897 --> 00:10:32,098
( Tarukus growls )

174
00:10:32,132 --> 00:10:33,099
( fangs crack )

175
00:10:33,133 --> 00:10:34,801
JoJo: YOUR TIME IS DONE.

176
00:10:34,901 --> 00:10:36,737
NOW I'LL ERASE YOU!

177
00:10:36,803 --> 00:10:38,104
Tarukus: ENOUGH OF YOUR BLATHER.

178
00:10:38,138 --> 00:10:39,640
YOU TALK TOO MUCH!

179
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:41,942
( spits )

180
00:10:41,975 --> 00:10:43,243
( roaring )

181
00:10:43,309 --> 00:10:45,378
JoJo: YOU'LL HAVE TO DO
BETTER THAN THAT!

182
00:10:49,149 --> 00:10:51,985
( yelling )

183
00:10:53,153 --> 00:10:54,320
Speedwagon: WELL PLAYED!

184
00:10:54,387 --> 00:10:57,323
♪

185
00:11:21,187 --> 00:11:23,189
JoJo: BARON ZEPPELI!

186
00:11:25,458 --> 00:11:26,860
SPEAK TO ME.

187
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,095
( Zeppeli gasping )

188
00:11:31,331 --> 00:11:37,037
JoJo: THIS IS ALL
SO TERRIBLY WRONG.

189
00:11:38,705 --> 00:11:41,942
WITHOUT YOU BESIDE ME,

190
00:11:42,008 --> 00:11:43,376
WITHOUT YOUR WISDOM
AND GUIDANCE,

191
00:11:43,476 --> 00:11:46,513
HOW WILL I MAKE MY WAY
THROUGH THIS WORLD?

192
00:11:46,547 --> 00:11:48,381
( Zeppeli gasps )

193
00:11:48,481 --> 00:11:53,053
JOJO, YOU SIMPLY
MUST PULL YOURSELF TOGETHER.

194
00:11:54,354 --> 00:11:57,490
YOU'VE NO TIME TO WASTE NOW.

195
00:11:59,059 --> 00:12:01,001
( gasps )

196
00:12:01,067 --> 00:12:03,570
YOU KNOW WHAT LIES AHEAD.

197
00:12:08,008 --> 00:12:10,744
NOW GO. LEAVE ME.

198
00:12:10,844 --> 00:12:13,814
SETTLE ACCOUNTS WITH DIO.

199
00:12:16,016 --> 00:12:17,918
BUT FIRST OF ALL,

200
00:12:18,018 --> 00:12:19,886
YOU MUST DESTROY THE MASK.

201
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,087
‐ ( gags )
‐ JoJo: ZEPPELI!

202
00:12:21,922 --> 00:12:24,090
( Poco crying )

203
00:12:25,191 --> 00:12:26,827
Zeppeli: PLEASE DON'T CRY.

204
00:12:28,228 --> 00:12:29,730
NO TEARS.

205
00:12:29,763 --> 00:12:32,833
I AM SATISFIED.

206
00:12:32,899 --> 00:12:35,201
I HAVE LIVED MY DESTINY.

207
00:12:35,268 --> 00:12:37,437
WHEN I WAS YOUNG,

208
00:12:37,504 --> 00:12:40,907
I WAS VERY HAPPILY MARRIED,

209
00:12:40,941 --> 00:12:43,109
BUT TO PURSUE THE MASK,

210
00:12:43,209 --> 00:12:46,613
I LEFT MY FAMILY BEHIND.

211
00:12:46,713 --> 00:12:51,384
HOWEVER, I'VE NEVER REGRETTED
THE CHOICE I MADE.

212
00:12:51,451 --> 00:12:55,121
I ACCEPT IT COMPLETELY.

213
00:12:57,858 --> 00:12:59,960
AND IT'S GOOD.

214
00:13:00,026 --> 00:13:02,302
IN THE END, I CAN SEE

215
00:13:02,368 --> 00:13:04,771
THAT MY CHOICE
WAS THE RIGHT ONE.

216
00:13:06,306 --> 00:13:11,411
JOJO, YOU ARE MY DELIVERANCE.

217
00:13:12,646 --> 00:13:13,814
BARON ZEPPELI.

218
00:13:13,914 --> 00:13:14,915
( Zeppeli chuckles )

219
00:13:14,981 --> 00:13:17,150
IT SEEMS TO ME THAT IN YOU

220
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:21,655
I HAVE FOUND BOTH
A BEST FRIEND AND A NEW FAMILY.

221
00:13:21,755 --> 00:13:27,828
JOJO, THROUGH YOU,
I WILL LIVE ON FOREVER.

222
00:13:27,928 --> 00:13:30,897
MY SON...

223
00:13:30,964 --> 00:13:32,465
JOJ‐‐

224
00:13:34,334 --> 00:13:35,769
( both gasp )

225
00:13:35,836 --> 00:13:37,938
♪

226
00:13:41,575 --> 00:13:43,677
Narrator:
THE 19th‐CENTURY NOVELIST

227
00:13:43,744 --> 00:13:47,247
WILLIAM MAKEPEACE THACKERAY
WROTE...

228
00:13:48,281 --> 00:13:51,818
"TO LOVE AND WIN
IS THE BEST THING."

229
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:58,424
"TO LOVE AND LOSE
IS THE NEXT BEST."

230
00:14:02,135 --> 00:14:07,207
AND SO IT WAS THAT JOJO
TOOK UP HIS MENTOR'S LIFE QUEST

231
00:14:07,273 --> 00:14:09,710
AS WELL AS HIS SPIRIT.

232
00:14:09,776 --> 00:14:11,712
♪

233
00:14:17,217 --> 00:14:20,386
JoJo: FAREWELL, MY FRIEND.

234
00:14:28,394 --> 00:14:30,897
( woman sobs )

235
00:14:30,964 --> 00:14:32,332
OH, PLEASE, SIR.

236
00:14:32,398 --> 00:14:36,169
I BEG YOU, PLEASE DON'T
BRING NO HARM TO MY CHILD.

237
00:14:36,236 --> 00:14:37,704
LET HIM BE.

238
00:14:37,738 --> 00:14:38,872
( gasps )

239
00:14:40,006 --> 00:14:40,907
Dio: HMM.

240
00:14:41,007 --> 00:14:43,076
DO I COMPREHEND YOU?

241
00:14:43,176 --> 00:14:45,579
LET US CLARIFY WHAT YOU DESIRE.

242
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:49,550
VOLUNTARILY YOU WILL
GIVE YOURSELF TO US

243
00:14:49,583 --> 00:14:53,153
ON THE CONDITION
THAT WE NOT TOUCH YOUR CHILD.

244
00:14:53,219 --> 00:14:55,255
IS THAT ACCURATE?

245
00:14:55,321 --> 00:14:57,824
( zombies growling )

246
00:15:01,267 --> 00:15:02,903
Woman: YES.

247
00:15:02,936 --> 00:15:05,171
ONLY DON'T HURT MY BOY.

248
00:15:05,238 --> 00:15:07,541
Dio: YOU MOVE ME TO TEARS.

249
00:15:07,608 --> 00:15:08,542
AGREED.

250
00:15:08,609 --> 00:15:10,376
YOU SHALL HAVE YOUR WISH.

251
00:15:10,443 --> 00:15:14,114
I HEREBY SWEAR THAT NEITHER I
NOR ANY OF MY SERVANTS

252
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:16,282
WILL BRING HARM TO YOUR CHILD.

253
00:15:16,349 --> 00:15:19,720
THAT SAID, YOU NEED
TO BE AWARE OF ONE THING.

254
00:15:19,786 --> 00:15:22,122
ALL MY MINIONS,
WITHOUT EXCEPTION,

255
00:15:22,222 --> 00:15:25,458
WILLINGLY GAVE UP
THEIR SOULS FOR ME.

256
00:15:25,526 --> 00:15:28,962
I TRULY THINK
IT WOULD WORK OUT FAR BETTER

257
00:15:29,062 --> 00:15:32,132
IF BOTH OF YOU WERE TO JOIN ME.

258
00:15:32,232 --> 00:15:33,967
THERE WOULD BE NO MORE WORRIES.

259
00:15:34,067 --> 00:15:37,571
YOU WOULD BOTH BE PART
OF A NEW AND GREATER FAMILY.

260
00:15:37,638 --> 00:15:40,440
Woman: REMEMBER, YOU PROMISED
NOT TO HURT MY CHILD.

261
00:15:42,042 --> 00:15:43,476
ME FOR HIM.

262
00:15:43,577 --> 00:15:45,445
Dio: SO BE IT THEN.

263
00:15:47,313 --> 00:15:48,481
( squelch )

264
00:15:48,549 --> 00:15:50,817
( blood pumps )

265
00:15:50,884 --> 00:15:52,786
( baby crying )

266
00:15:52,819 --> 00:15:53,787
( woman hisses )

267
00:15:56,890 --> 00:15:59,125
SWEET LITTLE CHILD.

268
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:00,667
( growls )

269
00:16:02,002 --> 00:16:03,003
( Dio chuckles )

270
00:16:03,103 --> 00:16:05,906
AS PROMISED,
WE'VE NOT HARMED THE CHILD.

271
00:16:05,972 --> 00:16:09,109
THAT'S SOMETHING YOU'VE
TAKEN CARE OF ON YOUR OWN.

272
00:16:12,112 --> 00:16:14,314
