00:16:19,686 --> 00:16:21,622
♪

276
00:16:27,694 --> 00:16:31,798
Speedwagon: 'STREWTH, JONATHAN'S
DEMEANOR IS DIFFERENT,

277
00:16:31,865 --> 00:16:35,201
AS IF THE SHUTTERS
