278
00:16:35,268 --> 00:16:37,303
AND THE SAME FOR ME.

279
00:16:37,370 --> 00:16:40,874
GOT NO TIME FOR TEARS,
ONLY ANGER.

280
00:16:40,974 --> 00:16:43,610
THERE'LL BE
PLENTY OF TIME TO CRY

281
00:16:43,677 --> 00:16:45,546
ONCE WE'VE DEALT WITH DIO.

282
00:16:45,646 --> 00:16:48,715
OI, JONATHAN,
DIO WAS SWANNING ABOUT,

283
00:16:48,782 --> 00:16:51,552
SAYING HE'D WIPE OUT THE TOWN
BY TOMORROW NIGHT.

284
00:16:51,652 --> 00:16:56,957
ZOMBIES WILL MULTIPLY, LIKE RATS
BREEDING IN A REFUSE HEAP.

285
00:16:57,023 --> 00:16:59,893
NO TELLING WHAT'S BEEN
GOING ON DOWN THERE.

286
00:16:59,993 --> 00:17:03,537
IS WIND KNIGHTS LOT
ALIVE OR UNDEAD?

287
00:17:03,570 --> 00:17:06,573
Poco: MY SISTER,
IS SHE ALL RIGHT?

288
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,008
JoJo: LET'S SEE.

289
00:17:09,375 --> 00:17:11,912
♪

290
00:17:13,213 --> 00:17:14,147
( Poco gasps )

291
00:17:14,214 --> 00:17:15,381
Speedwagon: EH?

292
00:17:15,415 --> 00:17:17,050
Poco: MR. ADAMS!

293
00:17:18,552 --> 00:17:20,086
Adams: WELL, POCO,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING

294
00:17:20,153 --> 00:17:22,756
AT THIS HOUR OF THE NIGHT
WANDERING THE MOORS?

295
00:17:22,823 --> 00:17:25,358
Poco: PLEASE, TELL ME,
IS EVERYONE ALL RIGHT?

296
00:17:25,425 --> 00:17:27,260
AND‐‐AND MY SISTER,
IS SHE SAFE?

297
00:17:27,327 --> 00:17:28,862
Adams: YOU DARE TO ASK?

298
00:17:28,929 --> 00:17:32,866
YOU MEAN TO SAY
YOU REALLY DON'T KNOW?

299
00:17:32,933 --> 00:17:34,100
( all gasp )

300
00:17:34,167 --> 00:17:35,902
‐ Adams: SHE'S BLOODY FURIOUS!
‐ ( cow moos )

301
00:17:35,936 --> 00:17:37,103
WHEN YOU GET HOME,

302
00:17:37,203 --> 00:17:40,106
SHE'S GONNA LOCK YOU IN THE BARN
AND TAN YOUR HIDE!

303
00:17:40,173 --> 00:17:41,341
‐ JoJo: UH...
‐ Poco: UH...

304
00:17:41,407 --> 00:17:43,243
JoJo: I GUESS
THAT MEANS SHE'S SAFE.

305
00:17:43,276 --> 00:17:44,545
Speedwagon: HUH. THEN LET'S GO.

306
00:17:44,611 --> 00:17:47,681
Poco: WELL,
THANK YOU, MR. ADAMS.

307
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:55,355
( Adams hisses )

308
00:17:55,421 --> 00:17:57,524
A NICE YOUNG CHILD.

309
00:17:57,591 --> 00:17:58,759
( cackles )

310
00:17:58,792 --> 00:18:02,936
I HAVE A TASTE
FOR SOME FRESH, WARM BLOOD.

311
00:18:02,969 --> 00:18:05,238
( laughs )

312
00:18:06,472 --> 00:18:07,908
‐ ( Poco wails )
‐ ( Speedwagon gasps )

313
00:18:07,974 --> 00:18:09,910
♪

314
00:18:11,645 --> 00:18:13,113
( Adams roars )

315
00:18:13,146 --> 00:18:14,981
JoJo: HE'S BEEN TURNED.
KEEP YOUR WITS ABOUT YOU.

316
00:18:15,081 --> 00:18:19,620
Adams: YOU CAN'T ESCAPE ME
WITH YOUR HUMAN SPEED!

317
00:18:21,221 --> 00:18:23,123
( JoJo yells )

318
00:18:23,156 --> 00:18:24,925
( Adams gasps )

319
00:18:29,495 --> 00:18:30,797
JoJo: THIS IS NO GOOD.

320
00:18:30,831 --> 00:18:32,633
WE'RE TOO LATE AGAIN.

321
00:18:32,666 --> 00:18:34,234
Man: THAT IS CORRECT.

322
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:36,670
♪

323
00:18:36,737 --> 00:18:38,338
THE VILLAGE IS LOST.

324
00:18:38,438 --> 00:18:40,173
THE ZOMBIES ARE EVERYWHERE.

325
00:18:41,642 --> 00:18:42,676
Poco: OH, NO.

326
00:18:42,776 --> 00:18:44,845
Speedwagon: NOT ANOTHER ONE.

327
00:18:44,945 --> 00:18:47,681
Dire: I'M KNOWN AS DIRE.

328
00:18:53,453 --> 00:18:56,289
JoJo: A KICK,
BUT WHY IS HE SO SLOW?

329
00:18:56,356 --> 00:18:57,524
( Dire grunts )

330
00:18:57,591 --> 00:18:58,925
( JoJo grunts )

331
00:19:01,134 --> 00:19:02,202
( gasps )

332
00:19:02,302 --> 00:19:03,336
Dire: TRY THIS!

333
00:19:03,369 --> 00:19:05,806
THE THUNDER SPLIT ATTACK!

334
00:19:11,678 --> 00:19:13,514
ARE YOU MAD, MAN?

335
00:19:13,547 --> 00:19:15,982
A NORMAL MAN WOULD PULL BACK,

336
00:19:16,049 --> 00:19:18,451
BUT INSTEAD
YOU WENT ON THE OFFENSIVE

337
00:19:18,519 --> 00:19:20,887
AND ATTACKED ME
WITH A HEAD BUTT.

338
00:19:21,988 --> 00:19:24,490
WAIT, PLEASE, JONATHAN JOESTAR,

339
00:19:24,558 --> 00:19:26,560
‐ I AM HUMAN.
‐ ( JoJo gasps )

340
00:19:27,493 --> 00:19:28,662
Dire: I APOLOGIZE.

341
00:19:28,729 --> 00:19:30,063
YOU MUST FORGIVE ME.

342
00:19:30,163 --> 00:19:32,799
I JUST WANTED TO SEE HOW WELL
ZEPPELI HAD TRAINED YOU.

343
00:19:32,866 --> 00:19:35,335
JoJo: WHAT?
DID YOU SAY, "ZEPPELI"?

344
00:19:37,504 --> 00:19:38,705
Dire: YOU HEARD CORRECTLY.

345
00:19:38,739 --> 00:19:41,207
ZEPPELI IS
A DEAR OLD FRIEND OF MINE.

346
00:19:41,241 --> 00:19:43,677
WE HAVE BEEN THROUGH
MANY TRIALS TOGETHER

347
00:19:43,744 --> 00:19:45,411
OVER THE PAST 20 YEARS.

348
00:19:45,478 --> 00:19:46,913
Man: THAT IS TRUE.

349
00:19:47,013 --> 00:19:48,414
♪

350
00:19:48,481 --> 00:19:51,317
HELLO. MY NAME IS STRAIZO.

351
00:19:51,384 --> 00:19:52,686
PLEASE READ THIS.

352
00:19:52,753 --> 00:19:55,255
JoJo: IT'S A LETTER.

353
00:19:55,321 --> 00:19:57,257
IT WAS WRITTEN BY...

354
00:19:57,357 --> 00:19:58,725
BARON ZEPPELI!

355
00:19:58,759 --> 00:19:59,893
( Speedwagon and Poco gasp )

356
00:19:59,926 --> 00:20:01,267
Straizo: WE'VE ONLY
JUST ARRIVED,

357
00:20:01,334 --> 00:20:04,204
BUT HE SENT THAT SOME TIME AGO
REQUESTING OUR AID.

358
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:07,941
HE WROTE ABOUT THE STONE MASK,
WHERE IT COULD BE FOUND,

359
00:20:08,008 --> 00:20:10,677
AND ESPECIALLY
ABOUT THE MAN WHO WEARS IT.

360
00:20:10,711 --> 00:20:12,846
Poco: EH, HUH?

361
00:20:12,879 --> 00:20:15,448
♪

362
00:20:15,516 --> 00:20:16,650
JoJo: HMM?

363
00:20:19,352 --> 00:20:21,054
‐ Dire: HMM?
‐ Straizo: MM.

364
00:20:21,154 --> 00:20:24,224
Dire: OUR TRAINING MASTER,
TONPETTY.

365
00:20:24,324 --> 00:20:26,292
( all gasp )

366
00:20:26,359 --> 00:20:28,228
( Tonpetty exhales )

367
00:20:28,328 --> 00:20:29,830
( gong reverberates )

368
00:20:29,896 --> 00:20:32,065
GREETINGS TO YOU ALL.

369
00:20:32,132 --> 00:20:37,203
JoJo: SO YOU'RE BARON ZEPPELI'S
TEACHER, MASTER TONPETTY.

370
00:20:38,639 --> 00:20:40,340
Tonpetty: MM...

371
00:20:43,176 --> 00:20:44,144
( JoJo gasps )

372
00:20:49,382 --> 00:20:51,885
IN THE REGION I CALL HOME,

373
00:20:51,918 --> 00:20:54,588
OUR CUSTOM IS
NOT TO SHAKE HANDS.

374
00:20:54,688 --> 00:20:57,223
IN THIS WAY,
WE GREET EACH OTHER.

375
00:20:57,257 --> 00:20:59,760
( all gasp )

376
00:21:05,572 --> 00:21:06,907
Tonpetty: WHERE IS HE?

377
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:09,610
ZEPPELI SHOULD BE HERE NOW.

378
00:21:12,112 --> 00:21:16,282
I SEE. ZEPPELI HAS
PASSED BEYOND THE VEIL.

379
00:21:16,349 --> 00:21:17,918
( Dire gasps )

380
00:21:17,951 --> 00:21:20,754
Tonpetty: EVEN IF
WE HAD ARRIVED EARLIER,

381
00:21:20,787 --> 00:21:23,890
HIS FATE WOULD STILL
HAVE BEEN THE SAME.

382
00:21:25,458 --> 00:21:26,860
HIS DEATH IS PROOF

383
00:21:26,927 --> 00:21:31,297
THAT THE STRENGTH
THIS DIO WIELDS IS DEVASTATING.

384
00:21:32,899 --> 00:21:37,871
HIS WICKEDNESS AND HIS POWER
ARE QUITE EXTRAORDINARY.

385
00:21:37,938 --> 00:21:39,873
♪

386
00:21:51,484 --> 00:21:52,653
( Dio chuckles )

387
00:21:52,753 --> 00:21:54,154
HOW AMUSING.

388
00:21:54,254 --> 00:21:57,423
I'VE PUT THIS TOWN IN MY THRALL
IN BUT A SINGLE NIGHT.

389
00:21:57,490 --> 00:21:59,425
( chuckles )

390
00:22:03,570 --> 00:22:05,672
♪

391
00:22:21,788 --> 00:22:24,991
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

392
00:22:25,025 --> 00:22:28,829
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

393
00:22:28,862 --> 00:22:34,134
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

394
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:36,637
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

395
00:22:36,703 --> 00:22:41,708
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

396
00:22:48,782 --> 00:22:52,118
♪ THE MUSIC DANCE AND SING

397
00:22:52,185 --> 00:22:55,822
♪ THEY MAKE THE CHILDREN
REALLY RING ♪

398
00:22:55,889 --> 00:23:01,067
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

399
00:23:01,167 --> 00:23:03,737
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

400
00:23:03,837 --> 00:23:07,741
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

401
00:23:07,808 --> 00:23:11,512
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

402
00:23:11,578 --> 00:23:13,647
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
OUT OF THE SKY ♪

403
00:23:13,714 --> 00:23:16,016
♪ AND THEY STAND THERE

404
00:23:18,919 --> 00:23:20,721
♪ ONE MILE OVER,
WE'LL BE THERE ♪

405
00:23:20,754 --> 00:23:22,523
♪ AND WE'LL SEE YOU

406
00:23:25,091 --> 00:23:29,095
♪ 10 TRUE SUMMERS, WE'LL BE
THERE AND LAUGHING, TOO ♪

407
00:23:31,331 --> 00:23:34,434
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE,
YOU'LL SEE ♪

408
00:23:34,535 --> 00:23:37,538
♪ I'LL BE THERE WITH YOU

409
00:23:38,605 --> 00:23:40,941
♪

410
00:23:41,041 --> 00:23:42,175
Creature: RUN, RUN, RUN!

411
00:23:42,242 --> 00:23:44,177
Dire: FELL FOR IT,
DIDN'T YOU, FOOL?

412
00:23:44,244 --> 00:23:46,913
Straizo: STRAIZO'S MY NAME.
NO MERCY.

413
00:23:46,947 --> 00:23:49,716
JoJo: I WILL FEEL NO HINT
OF GUILT FOR YOUR DEATH.

414
00:23:49,783 --> 00:23:51,552
Dio: COME, JOJO!

